text: Gold Coast could mean: ==Africa== * Ghana on the Gold Coast (region) in west Africa, which was made up of the following colonies: **Gold Coast (British colony), British colony on the Gulf of Guinea in west Africa **Brandenburger Gold Coast, former German colony **Danish Gold Coast, former Danish colony **Dutch Gold Coast, former Dutch colony **Portuguese Gold Coast, former Portuguese colony **Swedish Gold Coast, former Swedish colony ==Australia== * Gold Coast, Queensland, Australia
title: Gold Coast
